#

Sambar Delight (Onion-Free)

$15
350 kcal

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

IndianVegetarianComfort Food

Description

A comforting bowl of South Indian Sambar, rich in flavors, packed with lentils and veggies, and completely onion-free!

Ingredients

  • Toor Dal (Pigeon Peas): 1 cup
  • Mixed Vegetables (Carrot, Drumstick, Eggplant): 2 cups
  • Tomato: 1 large
  • Tamarind Paste: 1 tablespoon
  • Sambar Powder: 2 tablespoons
  • Turmeric Powder: 1/2 teaspoon
  • Curry Leaves: 10 leaves
  • Mustard Seeds: 1 teaspoon
  • Cumin Seeds: 1 teaspoon
  • Salt: to taste
  • Oil (Vegetable or Coconut): 2 tablespoons
  • Cilantro (for garnish): 2 tablespoons
